text: Cfut ar tameddurt n ddunit d urar kan, d zzhu, d acebbee, d zzux garawen, asuget n wayla akked derya. Am umedya ugeffur. Im$an is aaoben ijehliyen; sinna, ad isliwen, a ten twaliv ppiwoi$en; d$a ad eevmen. Di laxeot, aaaqeb uqsie akked ssmae s$uo Oebbi, akked llza. Tameddurt n ddunit d zzehwa kan ip$uooun
